## 🔹 Scenario 4: Go Binary
Developer gives you:
- Go source code

**Dockerfile (multi-stage):**
```dockerfile
FROM golang:1.22 AS builder
WORKDIR /src
COPY . .
RUN go build -o myapp

FROM alpine:latest
WORKDIR /app
COPY --from=builder /src/myapp .
EXPOSE 8080
CMD ["./myapp"]
```
Run:
```bash
docker build -t go-app .
docker run -p 8080:8080 go-app
```

